

     
       AR Rehman  has been chosen, alongwith a Finnish folk troupe, to  urlLink score the music  for the musical stage version of  The Lord of the Rings   "We are recreating Middle Earth and we needed the music that goes with it to be unique," said Kevin Wallace, who is producing the West End show.  "Rahman writes brilliant melodies with an exotic quality and we know he will write something which audiences will adore," he added.  Another feather in Rehman's already much-feathered cap!! 
     
    
